BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 1.882612 Tw (Most non-AI systems are built around authentication. A user logs in. Credentials are verified. Access is) Tj T* 0 Tw .016812 Tw (granted. From that point forward, the system assumes legitimacy. Every subsequent action is treated as valid) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.066159 Tw (because the session that enabled it was valid at the point it began. This assumption is false, and it is the) Tj T* 0 Tw (foundational governance failure of the vast majority of deployed non-AI systems.) Tj T* ET
Q
Q
q
