q
.058824 .098039 .137255 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 70.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .05262 Tw (Authentication answers one question: who are you? Authority answers a different question: should this action) Tj T* 0 Tw .786706 Tw (happen right now? These questions are not interchangeable. They address different conditions, at different) Tj T* 0 Tw -0.087688 Tw (moments, with different implications for whether an action is legitimate. Once access is granted, systems stop) Tj T* 0 Tw .120045 Tw (asking the second question. They proceed \227 because the first question was answered satisfactorily, and the) Tj T* 0 Tw (design assumption is that the answer to the first question also resolves the second.) Tj T* ET
