BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 1.487959 Tw (Authority is not something that can be added to a system later. It is not a feature that can be retrofitted) Tj T* 0 Tw .694549 Tw (through stronger authentication, better monitoring, or more comprehensive audit logging. It is a condition of) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.029952 Tw (operation \227 a structural requirement that must be present at the point of design, not appended as an) Tj T* 0 Tw (afterthought once the system is already deployed and the failure pattern is already established.) Tj T* ET
