q
1 0 0 1 68.3622 97.77953 cm
q
.058824 .098039 .137255 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 86.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 2.094775 Tw (A system that is built to continue will continue \227 even when conditions no longer justify its operation.) Tj T* 0 Tw .806636 Tw (Persistence is not neutral. It is directional. It pushes systems toward continuation in the absence of explicit) Tj T* 0 Tw .862149 Tw (instruction to stop. If authority validation does not exist at the point of execution, there is no mechanism to) Tj T* 0 Tw -0.082401 Tw (interrupt that continuation. The system does not pause. It does not reassess. It does not question. It proceeds) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.192275 Tw (\227 because proceeding is what it was designed to do, and nothing in its design recognises the difference) Tj T* 0 Tw (between proceeding under valid authority and proceeding under none.) Tj T* ET
