BT 1 0 0 1 0 70.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .262952 Tw (This is the same condition identified in automated AI systems, and it applies with equal force to deterministic) Tj T* 0 Tw .357299 Tw (systems. The difference is not in behaviour, but in perception. In deterministic systems, persistence appears) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.46748 Tw (as reliability. The system that has always processed this type of transaction continues to process it. The) Tj T* 0 Tw .207273 Tw (system that has always applied this rule continues to apply it. In reality, that continuation is not reliability \227 it) Tj T* 0 Tw (is continuity without validation.) Tj T* ET
