BT 1 0 0 1 0 70.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 1.529845 Tw (The longer a system operates without authority validation, the further it drifts from valid conditions. Each) Tj T* 0 Tw 1.300636 Tw (action is taken under assumptions that may no longer hold. Each outcome reinforces the illusion that the) Tj T* 0 Tw .244949 Tw (system is functioning correctly \227 because the outputs look like the outputs of a functioning system, because) Tj T* 0 Tw .310855 Tw (the system is operating consistently with its design, and because nothing in the system signals that anything) Tj T* 0 Tw (is wrong. Persistence without validation is the mechanism through which failure becomes continuous.) Tj T* ET
