1 0 0 1 68.3622 200.4567 cm
q
.058824 .098039 .137255 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 70.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .883805 Tw (Real control requires one condition: the system must be able to stop. Not eventually. Not after review. Not) Tj T* 0 Tw .627816 Tw (after escalation has run its course. At the moment of execution \227 at the exact point where consequence is) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.339879 Tw (created. Most systems cannot do this. They can log activity, flag anomalies, trigger alerts, and record) Tj T* 0 Tw .30848 Tw (outcomes. But they cannot prevent the action once execution has begun. The action happens. The record is) Tj T* 0 Tw (created after it has happened. The alert fires after the outcome is already in place.) Tj T* ET
