.058824 .098039 .137255 rg
BT 1 0 0 1 0 54.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL .733273 Tw (A system that fails due to its design requires a different response. It must be redefined \227 not patched, not) Tj T* 0 Tw .591015 Tw (monitored more closely, not audited more thoroughly, but fundamentally redesigned to incorporate authority) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.958263 Tw (validation at the point of execution. Until that redesign occurs, the failure will continue. Consistently,) Tj T* 0 Tw (predictably, and at whatever scale the system operates.) Tj T* ET
