BT 1 0 0 1 0 102.5 Tm /F1 9.5 Tf 16 TL 2.836182 Tw (A system without authority validation at execution cannot guarantee legitimacy \227 because legitimacy) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.619949 Tw (requires that authority exist at the moment of action, and that condition is never assessed. It cannot) Tj T* 0 Tw .261283 Tw (demonstrate accountability \227 because accountability requires a traceable human authority at the moment of) Tj T* 0 Tw 2.982136 Tw (action, and that trace cannot be established from a record that never captured it. It cannot prevent) Tj T* 0 Tw .464437 Tw (unauthorised action \227 because prevention requires a control mechanism at execution, and that mechanism) Tj T* 0 Tw .695906 Tw (is absent. And it cannot justify decisions under scrutiny \227 because justification requires demonstrating that) Tj T* 0 Tw (authority was present and valid, which the system has never been designed to prove.) Tj T* ET
